entry.value: delete from openiot.x002f where age(now(),date_trunc('minute', cast(recvtime as timestamp) + (interval '2 hour'))) >= '00:30:00.000000'

select cast(recvtime as timestamp) + (interval '2 hour') as FechaHora, entityid as Dispositivo, attrname as Atributo, cast(attrvalue as float) as Valor from openiot.x002f where attrtype = 'Number' and attrname not in ('n','d')

select date_trunc('minute',fechahora) - (CAST(EXTRACT(MINUTE FROM fechahora)AS integer)%10) * interval '1 minute' AS fechahora, dispositivo, atributo, avg(valor) as valor count(*) as cuenta FROM openiot.th_sensores GROUP BY date_trunc('minute',fechahora) - (CAST(EXTRACT(MINUTE FROM fechahora)AS integer)%10) * interval '1 minute' ,dispositivo,atributo GROUP BY date_trunc('minute',fechahora) - (CAST(EXTRACT(MINUTE FROM fechahora)AS integer)%10) * interval '1 minute' ,dispositivo,atributo;
